title: Big Ticket Abu Dhabi reveals Dh15 million jackpot, weekly wins for February
summary_full: Big Ticket Abu Dhabi's Series 260 offers a massive Dh15 million jackpot on March 3, 2026. February is already showering cash with daily e-draws, crowning a new winner every 24 hours.  Indian expat Hakkim Sha Habeeb was the first to win Dh50,000. Luxury car giveaways also add to the excitement this month.
